---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>Password Reset Sent</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Reset email dispatched. Await its arrival.">
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />

    <main class="confirmation-container">
      <h1>üß† A Reset Email Is En Route</h1>
      <p>
        If the email you entered corresponds to an account, a password reset link is now
        traveling through the vast ether of the internet toward your inbox.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please check your inbox (and perhaps your spam folder ‚Äî even good messages
        sometimes get lost in bad neighborhoods).
      </p>
      <blockquote>
        ‚ÄúRationality is not in avoiding failure, but in building systems that recover from it.‚Äù
      </blockquote>

      <div class="confirmation-links">
        <a href="/" class="link">‚Üê Return Home</a>
        <a href="/login" class="link">Login</a>
      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .confirmation-container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 4rem auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #fefcf8;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
    color: #333;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  blockquote {
    margin: 2rem 0;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    border-left: 3px solid #ccc;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #555;
  }

  .confirmation-links {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .link {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #0077cc;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>

